text:
Hey gang, I'm using a hubL variable to pull a blog post title and I'm able to get the title but it's not word wrapping correctly in my module. I think its with the &amp;nbsp; but I'm not to sure. Any ideas? or ways to replace the &amp;nbsp; with normal spaces?
```{{ recent_post.name }} 

&lt;!-- Outputs: What&amp;nbsp;is&amp;nbsp;video&amp;nbsp;blogging?--&gt;```

Finally solved it but I ended up using jquery
```$('h4.heading-with-border').each(function(){
    $(this).html($(this).html().replace(/&amp;nbsp;/gi,' '));
});```
